{"word":"ἀναγνάμπτω","slug":"ἀναγνάμπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναγνάμπτω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to bend back</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>αἰχμὴ ἀνεγνάμφθη</el> the spear-point <i>was bent back</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to undo, loose</i>, <el>δεσμόν</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}